      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why i'm still trying anymore. the nerve pain is just... it's constant. it's like being on fire every single second of the day and there's nothing the doctors can do to stop it. i'm just so exhausted from fighting it. it feels like i'm just trapped in a body that won't let me live.",
